    {
      "id": "chongqing-highlights",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Loved:\n + City skyline & Hongya Dong at night\n + Yangtze River cruise\n + Xiao Mian noodles (did not get to try the hotpot sadly)\n\nWe also ventured outside the main city area:\n + Chiyou Jiuli City\n + Three Natural Bridges",
